00:27:46.596 --> 00:27:47.196
Herr Song,

00:27:47.755 --> 00:27:49.315
Ich bin seitdem reifer geworden, okay?

00:27:49.356 --> 00:27:50.436
Gereift?

00:27:51.315 --> 00:27:52.956
